{"tid":809464,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"<Gimbal+Gopro 滑雪試拍分享>","createTime":"2018-09-07T08:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T11:11:05.000Z","uid":152232,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69ebaf8463042baf458859e4214dd22123eb9829","tid":809464,"uid":152232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"&lt;Gimbal+Gopro 滑雪試拍分享&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oVC-nBd_ahc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoVC-nBd_ahc&d=OZDGa8eCb4G2idw2znjWXDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=dd7019ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oVC-nBd_ahc</a><br />\n<br />\n上週末抽空試用了一下 Feiyutech 最新的 gimbal G6。老實說我是第一次用穩定器，所以也無從比較。因為毫無經驗，更加是一邊試一邊拍。<br />\n<br />\nCamera 是 Gopro Hero 5，設定是1080解像度，60FPS，和中度廣角。<br />\n<br />\n心得：<br />\n有 Gimbal 真的不一樣！我以前拍的片一直都畫面震的很利害，在減震這方面真的是爽，拍出來的畫面至少沒有那種地震感。難怪說用過 gimbal 就走不回頭了。<br />\n<br />\n拍得好不好，和器材當然有關，但始終拍攝技巧才是最重要。留意影片中，有的片段感覺較好，有的就怪怪的。主題能夠一直保持在中間，而畫面沒有突然大幅度移動的話就會較好。<br />\n<br />\n加上延長棍，由高一點的角度來拍也有很不錯的效果! 有些畫面甚至有點兒航拍的感覺呢。<br />\n<br />\n需然我沒用過其他 gimbal，G6 給我的感覺挺不錯，各種操作算易上手，電池續航力非常好，在低溫(-5℃)下用了大約3小時也只用了三分一不到的電。<br />\n<br />\nG6 也有time lapse功能, 試拍了一段: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/mmcNaeBNrEc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmmcNaeBNrEc&d=OZDGa8eCb4G2idw2znjWXDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=643123ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mmcNaeBNrEc</a><br />\n<br />\nP.S.<br />\n感謝世窗師兄們的幫忙<br />\n影片中是日常師兄姐們練習的狀況<br />\n當然仍有一大班其他厲害的高手<br />\n<br />\nG6 官方介紹: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/H1M-7Ef_HHc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FH1M-7Ef_HHc&d=OZDGa8eCb4G2idw2znjWXDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=e716693a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/H1M-7Ef_HHc</a><br />\nG6 Plus 官方介紹 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/xqloRKXmFGY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxqloRKXmFGY&d=OZDGa8eCb4G2idw2znjWXDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=404fe1ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xqloRKXmFGY</a>"},{"pid":"980e743b62f133fb038ad910743816e328ead329","tid":809464,"uid":56680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:31:08.000Z","msg":"留言支持下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望連登多 d 滑雪 post"},{"pid":"129d322785fc6b309c5594aae8853e20b73c5b4f","tid":809464,"uid":152232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"980e743b62f133fb038ad910743816e328ead329","tid":809464,"uid":56680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:31:08.000Z","msg":"留言支持下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望連登多 d 滑雪 post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"好呀! 我超鍾意滑雪!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c098ae88d5b3e1e25c829c092fdf38bc561e7f7c","tid":809464,"uid":152232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"980e743b62f133fb038ad910743816e328ead329","tid":809464,"uid":56680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:31:08.000Z","msg":"留言支持下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望連登多 d 滑雪 post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"Btw, 嚟緊坊間有幾個免費滑雪分享會<br />\n師兄有興趣嗎~?"},{"pid":"64300b395e88d23ab2dfa55eed7f166a7189bcaf","tid":809464,"uid":56680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c098ae88d5b3e1e25c829c092fdf38bc561e7f7c","tid":809464,"uid":152232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"980e743b62f133fb038ad910743816e328ead329","tid":809464,"uid":56680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T19:31:08.000Z","msg":"留言支持下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  希望連登多 d 滑雪 post"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T05:10:02.000Z","msg":"Btw, 嚟緊坊間有幾個免費滑雪分享會<br />\n師兄有興趣嗎~